query:
SELECT u.id, u.name, s.planId, p.displayName, p.toolsCount 
FROM users u 
LEFT JOIN subscriptions s ON u.id = s.userId 
LEFT JOIN plans p ON s.planId = p.id 
WHERE u.openId = (SELECT openId FROM users ORDER BY createdAt DESC LIMIT 1)
